    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7432202/" class="title-link">上海的演变过程就是对现代性的不懈追求？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7432202"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/68647784/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u68647784-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/68647784/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">楼后有一只喜鹊</span>
